{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":1}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席和我们一起合影","authors":["雷河清"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜悦的泪花在眼眶里转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的暖流在全身奔腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我胸中的激情啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在难以形容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是人生最幸福的时刻——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和我们一起合影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪花呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要蒙住我的眼睛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我仔细看看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席慈祥的面容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要这样剧烈的跳动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我静心倾听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席亲切的声音……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请您收下战士的“保证”："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“身在连队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心向北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远革命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着您指引的方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔往新的万里长征！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"DW：武汉部队"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}